{"tid":2218162,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"XPEV 小鵬 超低空飛行汽車","createTime":"2020-09-26T04:27:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T04:38:54.000Z","uid":167585,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ced608ae21418743db6f388b33a4bdd04587f2","tid":2218162,"uid":167585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWtUVKo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWtUVKo.jpg&h=4d4c322e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mwJqhXK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmwJqhXK.jpg&h=33ab9a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坦白講<br />\n我幾欣賞佢咁創新<br />\n不過我睇黎睇 點解覺得伏味咁濃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小鵬匯天成立7年，是中國新型飛行器設計規章的制定者。在現場，小鵬匯天的第一代飛行器也揭開面紗。何小鵬表示，飛行器2.0版本正在開發，將可乘坐兩人，可智能交互和低空地圖導航，垂直起降。在安全體繫上，它可以在5-25米超低空飛行，並進行自動駕駛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20200926/36449614.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.news.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20200926%2F36449614.html&d=I0uz%2BNPXkLchxl3mN3HTuxR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=5fc652f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.news.sina.com.tw/article/20200926/36449614.html</a>"},{"pid":"6a9dd753fe7e49f829cbd7ce12b24405c05c80e3","tid":2218162,"uid":209418,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"墜機嘅前奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47156dc37b371f4e52cd80e0da22422190624a49","tid":2218162,"uid":156375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a9dd753fe7e49f829cbd7ce12b24405c05c80e3","tid":2218162,"uid":209418,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"墜機嘅前奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />